# Copy to .env.local and fill in.
# This is a build-time variable — Vite inlines it into the bundle. The Client ID
# is a public identifier (not a secret), but committing it ties the repo to your
# specific Google Cloud project, so we keep it out of git.
#
# Get one at console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials → Create
# OAuth client ID → Web application. Set "Authorized JavaScript origins" to
# your Vercel URL plus http://localhost:5173 for local dev.
#
# See README.md → "Setup: Google OAuth" for the full walkthrough.

VITE_GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=
